(59, 38, 43, 40, '2020-12-09', NULL, '1:00', '1', 'Mallory\'s confidence is soaring (as it should be!), as was demonstrated by her mastery of exponential functions and their graphs.  We went through a set of review exercises in preparation for a test today, and we \"cleared every hurdle cleanly\"!  Mallory\'s explanations were so clear that I need to ask her permission if I can use them with other students. Would that be OK Mallory?  Please?  :) Mallory is a pleasure to work with, and her increased confidence is a sweet reward for me as her tutor.  Thanks Mallory!', '50', '2020-12-09 20:49:31', '2020-12-09 20:49:31'),
