(73, 38, 43, 40, '2020-12-16', NULL, '1:00', '1', 'There is absolutely no decay in Mallory\'s command of her math work from session to session.  No indeed! It\'s all growth, and we\'re not talking just linear growth. It \'s all exponential for Mallory!  In our session, we worked through a review packet on growth / decay functions.  Whether bacteria, population, or interest, Mallory handled it like a walk in the park.  Smooth, and no problem!  Great work Mallory!  I can\'t wait to hear about that super grade you are going to share with me at the next session.', '50', '2020-12-17 17:53:32', '2020-12-17 17:53:32'),
(74, 41, 53, 54, '2020-12-16', NULL, '1:00', '1', 'One proportion z interval, calculate and interpret confidence intervals, sample size needed given margin of error', '50', '2020-12-17 18:48:01', '2020-12-17 18:48:01'),
(75, 45, 45, 46, '2020-12-17', NULL, '1:00', '1', 'Creative Writing Prompt Warm-Up: Pretend you are one of Santa\'s elves. Write a journal entry about your day. Brendon completed the writing prompt and wanted to do a Part 2 later. The second half of the session consisted of grammar - focusing on the basic parts of speech. We reviewed noun, verb, adjective, adverb, preposition, interjection, article, and conjunction. He is most comfortable with nouns and adjectives right now. He learned the different types of verbs (action, linking & helping). Closing: Practiced labeling sentences with parts of speech.', '50', '2020-12-17 23:36:09', '2020-12-17 23:36:09'),
(76, 34, 58, 59, '2020-12-18', NULL, '1:00', '1', 'Reducing fractions, mixed numbers, initial evaluation.', '70', '2020-12-18 17:46:03', '2020-12-18 17:46:03'),
(77, 42, 44, 43, '2020-12-16', NULL, '1:00', '1', 'I helped Sam with a writing assignment for school, working with him on correcting spelling, punctuation, and sentence structure. His spelling is much improved, though he still needs help with some sight words.', '45', '2020-12-19 13:46:58', '2020-12-19 13:46:58'),
(78, 42, 46, 47, '2020-12-16', NULL, '1:00', '1', 'Zoe and I discussed the first three acts of Julius Caesar and broke down the rhetorical devices used in Brutus\' speech to the plebians. Zoe is deeply insightful in her character analysis and has taken to Shakespeare quickly.', '45', '2020-12-19 14:08:36', '2020-12-19 14:08:36'),
