(81, 42, 48, 49, '2020-12-22', NULL, '1:00', '1', 'Leena was dismissed from class early and we did some practice together with a multiplication card game. She is great with multiplying numbers by 1-5, but struggles with numbers over 5. However, she is able to slowly figure out more difficult problems and is more confident working through things.', '45', '2020-12-23 23:06:29', '2020-12-23 23:06:29'),
(82, 42, 46, 47, '2020-12-23', NULL, '1:00', '1', 'Zoe and I finished up work on Julius Caesar. She is enjoying Shakespeare and is already demonstrating a strong understanding of rhetoric and a stronger understanding of literary devices. We\'re going to continue with Shakespeare for a bit and read \"Much Ado About Nothing\" next.', '45', '2020-12-23 23:09:06', '2020-12-23 23:09:06'),
