(88, 38, 43, 40, '2021-01-06', NULL, '1:00', '1', 'Mallory came back strong after her holiday break, and transitioned into her work as smoothly as ever.  She shared with me the good news that her second attempt at a quiz produced great results, and I am sure that the first result was just an aberration for my star student.  Mallory\'s current work involved parabolas, intercepts, and elated equations, and as always, Mallory demonstrated her quantitative gifts.  It seems that Mallory will no longer have math after January, so our tutoring engagement may come to an end at that time,  All good things must come to an end.  I will miss Mallory :(', '50', '2021-01-07 17:24:52', '2021-01-07 17:25:58'),
