(167, 38, 43, 40, '2021-02-10', NULL, '1:00', '1', 'Mallory returned better than ever after a \"surgical detour\" to take on and vanquish the Khan Academy \"Course Challenge\" for Algebra 1.  It was totally Mallory\'s decision to subject herself to a review of a course she has already completed, and that says tons about her growth oriented attitude and natural desire to be the best that she can be. We decided that we may use a similar tool as a template to get a jump start on Geometry, or may just pick a few interesting topics to gain some preliminary exposure to the subject.  Whatever we decide, Mallory never fails to impress, and I consider it a gift to be able to guide her along whichever path she chooses.', '50', '2021-02-11 16:38:49', '2021-02-11 16:38:49'),
(168, 45, 45, 46, '2021-02-11', NULL, '1:00', '1', 'Creative writing prompt. Reviewed adjectives & adverbs. Continued learning the rest of the 8 parts of speech. Helping vs. linking verbs.', '50', '2021-02-11 22:41:41', '2021-02-11 22:41:41'),
(169, 42, 48, 49, '2021-02-09', NULL, '1:00', '1', 'I sat in on Leena\'s math class where they are continuing to practice multiplication and division skills. She continues to keep up nicely and her focus is hugely improved.', '45', '2021-02-12 18:02:50', '2021-02-12 18:02:50'),
(170, 42, 59, 61, '2021-02-09', NULL, '1:00', '1', 'Jackson and I organized his work for the week and we then worked together on his history and English homework. Jackson writes very well and demonstrated strong critical thinking skills. He seems to be enjoying his classes this semester already and hopefully, we can keep that up.', '45', '2021-02-12 18:07:39', '2021-02-12 18:07:39'),
(171, 42, 48, 49, '2021-02-10', NULL, '1:00', '1', 'Leena and I revisited time math this week. It\'s still conceptually challenging for her, but she\'s much improved from the last time we dealt with this subject.', '45', '2021-02-12 18:09:34', '2021-02-12 18:09:34'),
