(353, 38, 74, 71, '2021-05-05', NULL, '1:00', '1', 'It was a true pleasure to begin a tutoring engagement with Timur today, a bright young man who has uncharacteristically struggled the entire school year in Algebra 1.  After getting to know each other a bit, we went back to the beginning of the year in order to rebuild Timur into the confident math student that has been hiding. And Timur quickly revealed his true self, as we efficiently covered two school weeks of material in 40 minutes!  We not only covered it, but Timur learned it well and proved his proficiency at it.  By the end of the session, the new Timur had vanquished the old Timur, and a confident, enthusiastic, and fully capable young math wizard had emerged. Timur\'s Mom will speak to his teacher to see how we can leverage his \"new approach\" to Algebra 1 into an opportunity to get credit for late assignments, be granted extra time, and develop a realistic path to success in the course.  What was hiding has emerged! Timur  is on his way to success!', '50', '2021-05-06 13:18:25', '2021-05-06 13:18:25'),
(354, 41, 67, 68, '2021-05-08', NULL, '1:00', '1', 'rotational kinematics and dynamics ch9 drill', '50', '2021-05-10 00:29:20', '2021-05-10 00:29:20'),
