(356, 38, 74, 71, '2021-05-09', NULL, '1:00', '1', 'It was another dynamic session with Timur  today, as we did it again! We covered two weeks of material in one hour (that\'s 4 weeks in 2 sessions!) with the credit going to Timur and his great attitude, attentiveness, and high level of motivation. Despite my corny jokes, Timur rose to the occasion to become proficient in solving equations in one variable, independent of whether there were parentheses, items to combine, or fractions. And I still cannot process how quick this young man is in mental calculations involving integers and fractions! Timur, let your teacher know there\'s a new Timur in town, and we\'re coming to collect the highest grade we can get!', '50', '2021-05-10 14:02:45', '2021-05-10 14:02:45'),
(357, 60, 60, 62, '2021-05-12', NULL, '1:00', '1', 'Looked over Canvas. Couldn\'t check through the last quiz because it automatically locked, but we talked through the mistakes that she thought she made. Practiced multiplication.', '20', '2021-05-12 19:08:10', '2021-05-12 19:08:10'),
