(364, 38, 74, 71, '2021-05-12', NULL, '1:00', '1', 'Timur is my \"go to\" guy for adding integers and reducing fractions!  But that\'s just the beginning.  For the third session in a row, we progressed through 2 weeks of material in one hour, thereby getting Timur that much closer to his goals for this class.  With his humble demeanor and quiet confidence, Timur has emerged from whatever was holding him back, and is now well on his way to a successful outcome. And it is all because of his own talents, which he has finally shared with all of us! Timur is a marvel to watch, and I am enjoying every second of it.', '50', '2021-05-13 16:00:34', '2021-05-13 16:00:34'),
