(384, 38, 74, 71, '2021-05-19', NULL, '1:00', '1', 'We may not have covered 2 weeks of material in one hour today, but no one can say we did not make major progress! While Timur was continuing to dazzle me with his \"human calculator\" skills and his solutions to my riddles, I attempted to guide him through the analysis, set up and solutions of algebraic word problems. Timur is truly integrating this tool into his inventory, and with continued practice, it will become second nature.  We are on our way, and with each lesson, Timur\'s confidence shines brighter and brighter!  I so much enjoy my lessons with Timur!', '50', '2021-05-20 13:28:29', '2021-05-20 13:28:29'),
