(391, 38, 74, 71, '2021-05-23', NULL, '1:00', '1', 'Although today\'s topic of functions was somewhat more abstract than the material we have covered up to this point, Timur did a great job of hanging in there and letting the information gradually \"soak in\".  By the end of the lesson, he was \"fully functional\", and understood the four ways of presenting functions.  Although he did not have a joke to share with me, I attribute that to the fact we were back up to \"a week every half hour\" speed, and he just did not have time. Mom reassured me that Timur will pass the class, so our main goal is to get him caught up by the beginning of the next school year. If Timur continues to shine as he has been, we should have no problem with that objective.  Great work Timur!', '50', '2021-05-24 15:05:32', '2021-05-24 15:05:32'),
