(416, 38, 74, 71, '2021-05-30', NULL, '1:00', '1', 'Functions to the left! Functions to the right!  Timur is one of the most driven young men I have met in a long time. Although functions are giving him a bit of a tough time, he hangs in there, knowing that it is going to click sooner or later.  I am more than happy to try different approaches to clarify the concepts, because I know I have a motivated student who is eager to put the pieces together.  In each lesson, we try try to do a bit of review, and this should also facilitate Timur\'s quantitative growth. I cannot say enough how much I am enjoying our tutoring engagement.  Thank you so much Professor Timur!', '50', '2021-05-31 16:53:52', '2021-05-31 16:54:55'),
(417, 38, 74, 71, '2021-05-31', NULL, '1:00', '1', 'Today\'s session with Timur was a work of art!  By the end of it, Timur was clearly demonstrating that he had overcome whatever was bothering him about functions, and was handling the problems with confidence.  I was elated!  I am certain that with just a little bit more review and practice, \"function phobia\" will be a distant memory.  We then proceeded to begin the next unit, which appears to put functions under the microscope and focus on intervals.  Timur plans to work on the 2 assignments I gave him after yesterday\'s lesson, and Mom will let me know if she feels he could use even more practice.  Timur is doing super!', '50', '2021-05-31 18:51:07', '2021-05-31 18:51:07'),
