(643, 38, 56, 57, '2021-10-27', NULL, '1:00', '1', 'Ian has an exam tomorrow on sequences and linear regression, so we wisely used our session to focus on the review sheet provided by his teacher.  I do not remember covering such topics at this level of education, so the fact that Ian is understanding the concepts and applying them to actual problems is very impressive! Ian uses the sessions to gain focus and organization, and always comes out with more clarity by their conclusion.  Good luck tomorrow Ian! I am rooting for you and am confident you will do great!', '50', '2021-10-28 19:31:02', '2021-10-28 19:31:02'),
