(645, 60, 75, 72, '2021-10-22', NULL, '1:00', '1', 'Worked on proper capitalization and punctuation at the end of sentences. Reviewed picture charts, how to read them, and how to count by 2s.', '20', '2021-10-29 05:28:50', '2021-10-29 05:28:50'),
