(647, 42, 93, 90, '2021-10-27', NULL, '1:00', '1', 'Matthew and I had our first in-person session and it went very well. He was more focused and his work was more accurate than in our online sessions and I feel we\'re going to be able to do more and move faster now.', '54', '2021-10-29 20:34:57', '2021-10-29 20:34:57'),
(648, 42, 45, 46, '2021-10-29', NULL, '1:00', '1', 'Brendon and I began reading \"Boots on the Ground,\" a middle-reader book about US Soldiers\' experiences in the Vietnam War. We are reading the book out loud, stopping to decode difficult vocabulary words and discuss and analyze content. Brendon reads very quickly and sometimes skips over words, but was able to slow himself down as soon as I suggested. Analysis is still tricky for him, as he is very facts-oriented, but he\'s off to a good start.', '50', '2021-10-29 22:12:56', '2021-10-29 22:12:56'),
(649, 60, 75, 72, '2021-10-29', NULL, '1:00', '1', 'Reviewed contractions and did practice with contractions including \"not\".', '20', '2021-10-30 18:11:16', '2021-10-30 18:11:16'),
