(652, 38, 74, 71, '2021-10-31', NULL, '1:00', '1', 'Timur and I ended the month in style with an assignment involving graphing relationships and describing functions. Timur has  gotten so good, that we even felt confident in one of our answers in contrast to the answer that the teacher had as correct!  We then proceeded to the enrichment phase of the lesson, and applied Timur\'s skills to several \"graphing and interpreting functions\" problems.  Timur was running on all cylinders! Great job Timur!', '50', '2021-11-01 20:02:18', '2021-11-01 20:02:18'),
(653, 38, 89, 85, '2021-11-01', NULL, '1:00', '1', 'What a great session Sarah and I had today!  Sarah clearly identified and area in which she felt she needed some strengthening (i.e., single variable algebraic equations),  and together, we built up her skills to a true level of proficiency.  I am truly impressed with this young lady\'s willingness to identify a weak area.  But not only that, Sarah had no hesitation to confront it head on and do the necessary work to eliminate it.  Sarah IS truly gifted and talented, but well beyond mere academic parameters.  Great job Sarah!', '50', '2021-11-02 13:51:03', '2021-11-02 13:51:03'),
