(657, 34, 91, 88, '2021-11-03', NULL, '1:00', '1', 'Prep for upcoming test: solving equations in one variable, solving and graphing inequalities. Made Markus a list of steps to follow for solving equations, and asked his teacher if Markus can bring them to his test.', '79', '2021-11-03 18:50:01', '2021-11-03 18:50:01'),
(658, 38, 56, 57, '2021-11-03', NULL, '1:00', '1', 'I do not remember covering such topics when I was Ian\'s age.  Regression lines? Residual plots?  WOW!  And Ian is clearly demonstrating that he is up to the challenge.  In fact, Mom shared the great news that Ian earned a 30/30 on his recent exam.  Way to go Ian!  All I am doing is facilitating Ian\'s application of gifts and talents that he has always possessed!  And what an honor it is!  Today, Ian and I basically came up with a strategy to complete the homework assignment, for which Ian plans to do himself.  This young man has become quite independent.  No surprise though.  He is G and T through and through!', '50', '2021-11-04 16:34:24', '2021-11-04 16:34:24'),
(659, 60, 73, 67, '2021-11-04', NULL, '1:00', '1', 'Kept on reading \"Sam and the Firefly\". Learned five new letter combinations \"ew\", \"ow\", \"cr\", \"ck\", and \"er\". Practiced forming words with all of the combinations that we learned so far.', '20', '2021-11-04 22:34:01', '2021-11-04 22:34:01'),
