(667, 38, 89, 85, '2021-11-08', NULL, '1:00', '1', 'I have my work cut out for me to challenge Sarah with new material, as this young lady\'s gifts ensure that most things come to her easily.  Today, we ventured in to the world of areas, volumes, and surface areas, and as expected, it was in large part a review for my talented student.  Sarah informed me that she is finishing up the \"slopes\" unit, so I put her to the test with some challenging twists on finding slope.  Sarah did great, and I am honored to have an opportunity to work with her.', '50', '2021-11-09 14:37:12', '2021-11-09 14:37:12'),
