(670, 42, 93, 90, '2021-11-03', NULL, '1:00', '1', 'Matthew and I continued to work on complex multiplication problems. He is getting increasingly comfortable with 3 digit by 3 digit problems and we are going to begin working on division soon.', '54', '2021-11-10 17:59:47', '2021-11-10 17:59:47'),
(671, 42, 45, 46, '2021-11-05', NULL, '1:00', '1', 'Brendon and I continued reading \"Boots on the Ground,\" checking periodically for vocabulary comprehension and analyzing the story. Brendon needs to work on digging deeper when it comes to reading narratives. He has a great grasp of facts but struggles to articulate motivation.', '50', '2021-11-10 18:03:28', '2021-11-10 18:03:28'),
(672, 42, 93, 90, '2021-11-10', NULL, '1:00', '1', 'Matthew and I continued to work on multi-digit multiplication. He grasps the material conceptually but makes small mistakes that are definitely caused by his dysgraphia. We are developing strategies to help him catch these mistakes,  but he is concerned about how they will translate to taking tests online.', '54', '2021-11-11 02:29:40', '2021-11-11 02:29:40'),
(673, 38, 56, 57, '2021-11-10', NULL, '1:00', '1', 'Ian and I did some final prep before his regression exam tomorrow, and were guided by a review sheet provided by the teacher.  We reviewed predictions, residuals, and graphing, and by the end of the lesson, Ian had increased his confidence with the material.  Let\'s see,  He scored a 30/30 on his last exam.  Where can he go from here?  I hope there is some extra credit on the test.  It is not fair if the teacher does not give the student an opportunity to show how well he can do, which in Ian\'s case, has no limit!.', '50', '2021-11-11 15:05:40', '2021-11-11 15:05:40'),
(674, 42, 45, 46, '2021-11-12', NULL, '1:00', '1', 'Brendon and I continued reading through \"Boots on the Ground\" and going over vocabulary and comprehension questions. I want to shift to a narrative book with him, so next week we\'re going to start reading \"War Horse\" by Michael Morpurgo.', '50', '2021-11-12 23:53:28', '2021-11-12 23:53:28'),
(675, 42, 96, 92, '2021-11-12', NULL, '1:00', '1', 'Drew and I spent some time getting to know each other a bit before we began working through his homework for Macbeth. We watched some clips from the Ian McKellen/Judi Dench film to enhance his experience of the play. Drew is also extremely interested in geography, so we looked at some of the locations pertinent to the play. Drew is very literal but is able to analyze with relative ease when pressed. I think I should be able to help him.', '54', '2021-11-12 23:55:50', '2021-11-12 23:55:50'),
(676, 60, 73, 67, '2021-11-09', NULL, '1:00', '1', 'Completed a worksheet that had Brynn match a drawing to the first two consonants that it started with. Had her read all of them before looking at the pictures for practice. Continued with reading \"Sam and the Firefly\". In addition to working on getting faster on reading and being able to identify patterns in words, also started to make predictions about what will happen in the text. Finished with a couple minutes of basic addition practice.', '20', '2021-11-15 04:32:42', '2021-11-15 04:32:42'),
(677, 60, 66, 67, '2021-11-09', NULL, '0:30', '0.5', 'Practiced multiplication with 8s and actually memorizing it instead of counting up each time. Looked over all assignments from class and worked on correcting addition/subtraction mistakes.', '20', '2021-11-15 04:34:01', '2021-11-15 04:35:47'),
(678, 60, 60, 62, '2021-11-11', NULL, '1:00', '1', 'Did some practice with multiplication. Looked over packet from school and worked on math homework for ratios and finding unit price.  Started talking about negative numbers and basic prealgebra.', '20', '2021-11-15 04:34:55', '2021-11-15 04:34:55'),
(679, 38, 74, 71, '2021-11-14', NULL, '1:00', '1', 'Timur continues to build himself up week by week - but this young man is no house of cards!  He is as solid as ever!  This evening we reviewed and mastered slope-intercept and standard forms for the equation of a line. Timur was able to convert from one to the other, and was quite confident by the end of the session.  And he should be! He is a gifted young man.  Great work Timur!', '50', '2021-11-15 23:09:37', '2021-11-15 23:09:37'),
