(687, 38, 56, 57, '2021-11-17', NULL, '1:00', '1', 'Ian and I merged several critical concepts this evening, as we connected constant difference, slope, and average rate of change.  The materials that Ian is provided are far from user friendly, but together, we \"crack the code\" and learn the critical concepts.  Ian may sometimes enter the session with some gaps in his knowledge, but after he fully engages himself and puts in the effort, he is \"up to speed\"  .  He truly transforms himself before my eyes.  Great work Ian! Thanks for getting me \"up to speed\" in \"game theory\".', '50', '2021-11-18 23:33:35', '2021-11-18 23:33:35'),
