(693, 38, 74, 71, '2021-11-21', NULL, '1:00', '1', 'Timur came to this evening\'s session  with one whopper of a problem concerning rates of change.  From the onset, we realized how difficult a task we faced in interpreting the problem  As giving up was not an option, we gave alternative responses based on different interpretations of what was meant. It was not as satisfying as knowing we nailed it, but we accepted the fact that it was the best we could do.  Timur and I made peace with the fact that we will sometimes have days such as this.  Good work Timur!', '50', '2021-11-22 17:30:54', '2021-11-22 17:30:54'),
