(695, 38, 89, 85, '2021-11-22', NULL, '1:00', '1', 'After demonstrating, last week,  her proficiency in the substitution method for solving systems of linear equations, Sarah carried the momentum into this week and handily did the same with the substitution method. I hope i will eventually see a \"threepeat\"  for Gaussian Elimination and Cramer\'s Rule.  I am not sure we will get to those latter two so soon though.  Nevertheless, Sarah continues to amaze me with her ability to quickly learn and apply new concepts.  She is a rising star!', '50', '2021-11-24 02:53:23', '2021-11-24 02:53:23'),
