(699, 94, 98, 95, '2021-11-23', NULL, '1:00', '1', 'I worked with Mason on a worksheet all about the history of anime because he likes anime. We worked through the hard words in the reading and answered comprehension questions. I had him design his own anime character, label it, and think of adjectives explaining it.', '25', '2021-11-28 23:48:02', '2021-11-28 23:48:02'),
(702, 38, 74, 71, '2021-11-28', NULL, '1:00', '1', 'I would describe my session with Timur this week as \"refreshing\", as the instructions were clear and we felt confident with our methodology.  Timur was on break from school, but Mom wanted to make sure that Timur\'s skills remain \"fresh\" .  The review was constructive for Timur, who may have become a bit rusty with the material we covered: solving simultaneous equations.  By the end of the session, Timur was \"refreshed\" and feeling better about his abilities. He is doing very well.  Good work Timur!', '50', '2021-11-29 16:09:35', '2021-11-29 16:09:35'),
