(842, 38, 56, 57, '2022-02-02', NULL, '1:00', '1', 'Their was magic in the air, as everything worked out perfectly in my session with ian today. He was super focused,  could make no mistakes, and truly demonstrated the levels to which he can rise. The focus of our work was absolute value functions, and whether we graphed them or solved them algebraically, Ian was flawless.  I could not help but be elevated myself, seeing firsthand what this young man is capable of doing.  Keep it up Ian!', '50', '2022-02-03 16:44:08', '2022-02-03 16:44:08'),
