(844, 38, 43, 40, '2022-02-03', NULL, '1:00', '1', 'Stop....in the name of the law (of sines)!  Mallory certainly stopped long enough to show that she had mastered this useful geometric law, and allowed me to understand aspects of it that I had never focused on before.  Thanks for the assist Mallory!  My dear student made a special request at the end of the session to review how to find the area of a triangle.  I was happy to oblige.  Have a great week Mallory!', '50', '2022-02-04 14:56:35', '2022-02-04 14:56:35'),
