(928, 60, 60, 62, '2022-03-03', NULL, '1:00', '1', 'Reviewed figurative language and worked on creating a quizlet to study. Worked on math homework that had operations with decimals.', '20', '2022-03-06 18:16:28', '2022-03-06 18:16:28'),
