(945, 94, 45, 46, '2022-03-10', NULL, '1:00', '1', 'Today, we worked on conjugating verbs and putting them in a sentence with a person, verb, object, and adjective. I felt that the homework that the teacher gave him was a little bit too over his Spanish level. I tried to break it down as best possible, and he was catching on! Overall, it was a productive class.', '35', '2022-03-11 00:08:47', '2022-03-11 00:08:47'),
(946, 38, 56, 57, '2022-03-09', NULL, '1:00', '1', 'Ian and I felt as if we were in navigation mode this evening, as we spent our time getting familiar with and practicing horizontal and vertical translations.  In addition, we became proficient at expressing these transformations in functional form.  Ian gave extra focusing effort during the session, and it paid off with new skills in his inventory.  Great job Ian!', '50', '2022-03-11 00:10:20', '2022-03-11 00:10:20'),
