(1370, 38, 119, 114, '2022-11-09', NULL, '1:00', '1', 'Michael and I made a major breakthrough today in communicating clearly so as to maximize our utilization of each session. I understand much better his position and needs, and look forward to enhancing my support. He has several gaps to fill, which have resulted from advancement to 5th grade math without the benefit of having experienced 4th grade math. He is a smart young man and should be able to bridge the divide without significant difficulty.', '50', '2022-11-10 20:48:47', '2022-11-10 20:48:47'),
(1371, 38, 74, 71, '2022-11-09', NULL, '1:00', '1', 'Timur and I prepared for an exam that he has tomorrow in geometric proofs concerning triangle congruence.  By breaking down the process and reviewing the fundamentals, Timur was able to make significant progress.  He is certainly on the road to success!', '50', '2022-11-10 20:51:03', '2022-11-10 20:51:03'),
(1372, 38, 111, 109, '2022-11-09', NULL, '1:00', '1', 'Mason and I continued our quest to master rigid transformations and congruence.  My super student is truly flexing his \"geometry muscles\" and is clearly climbing the learning curve.  It is quite inspiring to see his confidence grow before my eyes.  Mason is on the right track!', '50', '2022-11-10 20:59:06', '2022-11-10 20:59:06'),
