(1404, 94, 45, 46, '2022-12-01', NULL, '1:00', '1', 'Today we did a lesson on \"palabras de frecuencia\" or frequency words, so adverbs used to describe frequency like always, almost always, usually, never, etc. We made sentences and practiced pronunciation. Lastly, I taught him some memorization techniques that helped me in nursing and Spanish. Sometimes, you have to think of silly things to remember words. Ex. Picante= spicy, pica= it burns, think of Pikachu eating a spicy pepper saying, \"pica, pica, pica!\".', '45', '2022-12-02 00:06:56', '2022-12-02 00:06:56'),
