(1416, 38, 74, 71, '2022-12-07', NULL, '1:00', '1', 'Timur and I sometimes have to be creative to figure out what should be the focus of the session, but we always come up with something relevant and instructive.  This evening, we delved into similar triangles, their properties, and worked on some challenging problems.  Timur was on his game!', '50', '2022-12-08 14:47:22', '2022-12-08 14:47:22'),
