(1418, 94, 45, 46, '2022-12-08', NULL, '1:00', '1', 'Today, we learned about reflexive verbs. \"Doing something to one\'s self\" Its a tricky part of the Spanish language. We watched a video and did exercises on it. Brendon caught on pretty fast and this is a concept very different from the English language. I am excited for next week\'s reflexive lesson because I have a fun lesson planned!', '45', '2022-12-09 00:03:31', '2022-12-09 00:03:31'),
