(1439, 38, 74, 71, '2022-12-20', NULL, '1:00', '1', 'Timur\'s birthday is tomorrow, so I was happy to reschedule this week\'s session  to today so that he can celebrate without interruption. Today\'s highlights included the Pythagorean Theorem, and determining if a set of three side lengths can form a right triangle.  My super student was on his game, and can go into the break feeling good about his progress.  Happy birthday Timur!', '50', '2022-12-21 15:42:35', '2022-12-21 15:42:35'),
