(1445, 38, 74, 71, '2022-12-28', NULL, '1:00', '1', 'Timur was on his game this evening in an unexpected \"holiday\" session. He came willing to work, and was extremely productive,  We covered triangle concepts from A-Z as a way to send him back to school after the break with fortified foundations.  I was proud of my super student this evening.  Great work Timur!', '50', '2022-12-29 14:51:02', '2022-12-29 14:51:02'),
(1446, 115, 48, 49, '2023-01-03', NULL, '1:00', '1', 'Leena and I worked through her homework for the week, which was on the multiplication of mixed number fractions in word problems and with models.', '30', '2023-01-03 23:00:07', '2023-01-03 23:00:07'),
(1447, 94, 45, 46, '2023-01-03', NULL, '1:00', '1', 'Today, we reinforced the difference between infinitive form of verbs and reflexive, and how some verbs can be both. We practiced reflexive verbs and I had him act them out with his Pikachu figuirine. We practiced for his presentation tomorrow on reflexive verbs and times of the day.', '45', '2023-01-03 23:59:17', '2023-01-03 23:59:17'),
(1448, 38, 74, 71, '2023-01-04', NULL, '1:00', '1', 'Timur is moving forward at a rapid pace, as we entered full force into trig and triangle concepts.  My super student put in a great effort this evening, and was rewarded with a solid grasp of the fundamental ideas and solution methodologies.  Great work Timur!', '50', '2023-01-05 14:59:46', '2023-01-05 14:59:46'),
(1449, 96, 112, 110, '2023-01-04', NULL, '1:00', '1', 'Division word problems and averages', '20', '2023-01-05 21:01:51', '2023-01-05 21:01:51'),
(1450, 96, 62, 64, '2023-01-05', NULL, '0:30', '0.5', 'Review of slope for upcoming midterm', '20', '2023-01-06 02:36:15', '2023-01-06 02:36:15'),
(1451, 38, 56, 57, '2023-01-05', NULL, '1:00', '1', 'Welcome back Ian!  As my super student did not have any assigned work to review, we improvised a review of our own, including problems involving extrema, domains, ranges, and intercepts  (Thank you Mathia!).  Ian showed me some of his \"gains\" from the holiday  season; he made out quite well.  I look forward to resuming our climb up the learning curve and the confidence that it will bring.', '50', '2023-01-06 15:36:43', '2023-01-06 15:36:43'),
(1452, 60, 60, 62, '2023-01-05', NULL, '1:00', '1', 'Developed a study plan for upcoming social studies test on the Crusades. Reviewed negative number and ratio math concepts through Canvas module.', '30', '2023-01-07 21:18:11', '2023-01-07 21:18:11'),
(1453, 60, 66, 67, '2023-01-05', NULL, '0:30', '0.5', 'Worked on school math homework with long division, Used two methods, either regular long division or splitting the dividend into two sums, dividing those and adding the quotients together. Discovered how multiplication can be used to check division.', '30', '2023-01-07 21:20:08', '2023-01-07 21:20:08'),
(1454, 60, 73, 67, '2023-01-05', NULL, '0:30', '0.5', 'Completed a writing prompt about winter break. Practiced repeated addition of 2s, 3s, 5s, and 10s. Practiced adding and subtracting 2 digit numbers with and without regrouping both in mental math and tabular addition.', '30', '2023-01-07 21:22:06', '2023-01-07 21:22:06'),
(1455, 96, 62, 64, '2023-01-08', NULL, '1:00', '1', 'Preparation for midterms: solving two-step inequalities, estimating radicals, and properties of exponents', '20', '2023-01-08 17:05:54', '2023-01-08 17:05:54'),
(1456, 94, 45, 46, '2023-01-08', NULL, '1:00', '1', 'Today, we worked on Brendon\'s homework of reflexive verbs, daily routine, and telling time. I taught him some tricks for telling time and about remembering the word breakfast. It was a productive day and I loved seeing Brendon excel at reflexive conjugations!', '45', '2023-01-09 00:52:50', '2023-01-09 00:52:50'),
(1457, 34, 45, 46, '2023-01-09', NULL, '1:00', '1', 'Writing and solving two step equations from word problems.', '75', '2023-01-10 01:13:51', '2023-01-10 01:13:51'),
(1458, 38, 111, 109, '2023-01-09', NULL, '1:00', '1', 'Welcome back Mason!  And just in time to prepare for an upcoming exam on transformations and similarity! My super student rose to the task and handled most of the questions singlehandedly.  Great job Mason!  You should feel confident going into the exam.', '50', '2023-01-10 15:57:11', '2023-01-10 15:57:11'),
(1459, 60, 118, 114, '2023-01-09', NULL, '0:30', '0.5', 'Reviewed school homework from last week. Practiced factoring 20 and repeated addition as multiplication, Reviewed two digit numbers, will continue next week and review regrouping.', '45', '2023-01-10 18:50:44', '2023-01-10 18:50:44'),
(1460, 60, 119, 114, '2023-01-09', NULL, '0:30', '0.5', 'Practiced 6s and 7s multiplication tables through fast facts. Reviewed adding and multiplying fractions, finding equivalent fractions, and changing fractions from mixed numbers to improper fractions.', '45', '2023-01-10 18:51:33', '2023-01-10 18:51:33'),
(1461, 60, 75, 72, '2023-01-09', NULL, '1:00', '1', 'Read chapter one of \"Class Pets: Fuzzy Freaks Out\" and wrote a one paragraph summary of the chapter.', '30', '2023-01-10 18:57:07', '2023-01-10 18:57:07'),
(1462, 94, 45, 46, '2023-01-10', NULL, '1:00', '1', 'Today, we reviewed reflexive, clothing vocab, seasons, telling time, and daily routine. We practiced describing our days using this vocab. We reinforced the difference between reflexive and present or past regular verbs.', '45', '2023-01-11 01:14:16', '2023-01-11 01:14:16'),
(1463, 38, 74, 71, '2023-01-11', NULL, '1:00', '1', 'As a way to prepare for Timur\'s upcoming geometry test, we used the NY State Regents Geometry exam to review concepts and practice problems.  My super student was able to refresh many ideas that had been dormant for awhile, and should feel confident in his prospects for success. I am rooting for you Timur!', '50', '2023-01-12 17:59:41', '2023-01-12 17:59:41'),
(1464, 96, 62, 64, '2023-01-12', NULL, '0:30', '0.5', 'Extra credit quiz', '20', '2023-01-12 21:30:24', '2023-01-12 21:30:24'),
(1465, 38, 56, 57, '2023-01-12', NULL, '1:00', '1', 'Ian and I were equal partners this evening (as we have become much more often lately), as we worked on multiplying binomials with the \"box\"? method, as well as synthetic division.  It is quite inspiring to see my super student\'s growth occurring right before my eyes.  Keep it going Ian!', '50', '2023-01-13 15:10:21', '2023-01-13 15:10:21'),
