(1476, 38, 74, 71, '2023-01-18', NULL, '1:00', '1', 'By Timur\'s request, we surged ahead into a review of circle fundamentals, which included a detailed look at chords and chord theorems. Timur impressed me with his desire to advance and his active collaboration in solving problems.  My young student is climbing the learning curve...and more!', '50', '2023-01-19 17:57:27', '2023-01-19 17:57:27'),
