(1480, 38, 56, 57, '2023-01-19', NULL, '1:00', '1', 'I am happy to report that ian is now quite proficient in synthetic division. Its application may be limited, and doing several problem is sequence may get a bit grueling, but one cannot deny that my super student can now confidently declare that he knows how to deal with any synthetic division problem that is dealt to him.  Another weapon added to his quantitative arsenal!  Great job ian!', '50', '2023-01-20 15:04:44', '2023-01-20 15:04:44'),
(1481, 60, 60, 62, '2023-01-19', NULL, '1:00', '1', 'Went through Canvas and identified remaining deadlines for this quarter. Practiced for math test and adding and subtracting negative numbers.', '30', '2023-01-20 16:31:49', '2023-01-20 16:31:49'),
(1482, 60, 73, 67, '2023-01-19', NULL, '0:30', '0.5', 'Reviewed coins and how to make different amounts with coins (ex. 59 cents could be 2 quarters, a nickel and 4 pennies). Did a couple easy sudoku puzzles to break up the time.', '30', '2023-01-20 16:33:13', '2023-01-20 16:33:13'),
