(1492, 38, 56, 57, '2023-01-26', NULL, '1:00', '1', 'Ian and I continued our journey through trigonometry, with my super student demonstrating a solid grasp of the concepts and a confident ability to apply them. We worked through problems involving solving for sides ,and angles, and Ian truly shined.  It is very inspiring to see this young man to continue to grow in his skills and confidence.', '50', '2023-01-27 20:02:05', '2023-01-27 20:02:05'),
(1493, 94, 45, 46, '2023-01-29', NULL, '1:00', '1', 'Today, we practiced Brendon\'s vocab words, reading comprehension, and listening skills. I made up 4 different people and repeated their stories twice in Spanish, then asked Brendon questions about each person. I taught Brendon how I do reading and listening comprehension exams and my strategy of jotting down ONLY the important parts of the listening segments, to avoid missing important information. This is a good skill in interviewing and talking to people as well.', '45', '2023-01-29 18:00:52', '2023-01-29 18:00:52'),
