(1501, 94, 45, 46, '2023-02-02', NULL, '1:00', '1', 'Today we reviewed items of clothing in Spanish, we practiced putting together outfits for different occasions in Spanish, and learned sports in Spanish. We then learned about different habitats and played a game of \"I\'m thinking of a habitat\" in Spanish. We learned many animals of the forest and the jungle. We learned about the Amazon rainforest towards the end of class just for fun and so he gets excited about traveling there one day to practice his Spanish!', '45', '2023-02-02 23:59:59', '2023-02-02 23:59:59'),
