(16, 'Vlad', NULL, 'admin', 'vgutkovsky@yahoo.com', '$2y$10$0xVvdVleRVQeJdgn.iGjJOWMsPehBDO4A2THvGFn2EoEIvlEbZWbq', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Pacific Time', 'active', '1234567890', 'profile-1602173325-349395.jpg', 'Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat. Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat. Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat.', 'Subscribe', 'g8gR7wdo1vqAGy8vA2yjGPcPhcFCNQSH2zaPOsOyVv99prD80k0iFAd7jE1v', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2020-06-29 16:12:02', '2023-08-15 02:27:22'),
(34, 'Sofi', 'Fedushchenko', 'admin', 'sofi@smartcookietutors.com', '$2y$10$Zhg2z03ejCC5wE4vH9GZfOA0eB26u.kxGfJmAwhHDXxRGeD4yWLie', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Eastern Time', 'active', '443-574-4682', 'profile-1602259346-412594.jpg', 'Becoming a math teacher is what I was meant to do. Following in the footsteps of my grandmother, a master teacher who instilled in me an appreciation for learning and for math in particular, I gently found my way to teaching after earning a degree in math and computer science and embarking on a career as a software developer. Teaching wasn’t on my radar until, by a series of coincidences, I got a job teaching dance in a local studio on the weekends. That was when I realized teaching was in my blood. I went on to earn a master’s from the University of Michigan in Secondary Math Education which took me to Chicago where I spent a few years teaching in an inner city charter high school as well as a private middle school for gifted children.\r\n\r\nNow back in my native Maryland, I am thrilled to work with students of all ages and levels. For me, there is no greater satisfaction than watching a student’s confidence grow as his or her skills improve – being a part of that process is wonderfully fulfilling. I look forward to working with you!', 'Subscribe', 'P0Hqjs1xO2DBUMOjV2kt1YiIjVQr5Y58s4sJmorCNyiVBarajAYVbYn42MuT', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2020-10-09 21:00:10', '2026-03-26 23:49:20'),
(35, 'Annie', 'Pitts', 'customer', 'annie102582@gmail.com', '$2y$10$iXc6DzzB3558faC86CyP9eWllycGOr6q/Xa3v5LzRF31164q23Xpe', '4921 Ellis Lane', 'Ellicott City', 'Maryland', '21043', 'Eastern Time', 'active', '4109254564', NULL, NULL, 'Subscribe', '5hyQ12CDF9JRTrXgCh91t5sRlAQqkt2JxUJ3YcYfORI1AytpixID8mlYJR70', 'cus_SIipVX84nG7Zx5', 'MasterCard', '3869', 'tok_1RO7NrEjbxiB0vaP8v5V0xEd', '2020-10-09 16:23:34', '2025-05-13 01:11:55'),
(38, 'Jeffrey', 'Katz', 'tutor', 'tutorrouter@gmail.com', '$2y$10$0AVJOGAq3JRHrs1ldhwzpOBsFAdZyYMWuSQLuE6xV/NO4xCuEJWhq', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Eastern Time', 'inactive', '443-850-5010', 'profile-1605487481-529527.jpeg', 'Hi. I look forward to sharing my knowledge with you to assist you in becoming the best you can be.\r\n\r\nI have a B.A. in Applied Mathematics (including Statistics) and Economics from The Johns Hopkins University, where I graduated with a 3.96 GPA and earned admission into the Phi Beta Kappa Honors Society. I also have an MBA in Finance and Public Policy from The Wharton School, where I earned admission into the Beta Gamma Sigma Honors Society. I have taken two SAT prep courses, with transferable skills to the ACT, GMAT, GRE, ASVAB and other standardized tests. I have been a Certified Financial Planner and Chartered Financial Consultant, and have been in the financial services industry for over 27 years.\r\n\r\nPeople of all ages feel comfortable with me immediately. I have 4 children of my own (ages 19-29) (AND NOW 3 GRANDCHILDREN!), and kept my tutoring skills very sharp on a nightly basis! I was extremely successful in customizing my approach to each member of that crew, so I can certainly do it for you or your child. Let\'s put it this way: They would \"rehire\" me every night, so I must have done something right!\r\n\r\nI would love to assist you. Thank you for your consideration.', 'Subscribe', '8X6lTiipCKaaOfV4ZkbwcJL7QrPZ0N075ojrLYbLV0pPIa8PvrLeowpbK50C', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2020-11-11 21:34:43', '2025-02-04 01:29:12'),
(39, 'Fireflies', 'Glow', 'customer', 'sofifed@gmail.com', '$2y$10$LFhWi2RhLFSMGLRDeQbB/eVHBOE7HnhAA0wywjnt.cpeorYcNk5ru', '5000 House Court', 'Seattle', 'Maryland', '21048', 'Eastern Time', 'active', '410-555-5555', NULL, NULL, 'Subscribe', 'oVatURhwJoXaNKhMzH9lH4uVaHf8qVGayvv3ysf999h3k1zUWKomjDKZVpbG', 'cus_IPVjidDI1MjaAU', 'American Express', '2008', 'tok_1HoghyEjbxiB0vaPwzfasF7G', '2020-11-11 16:05:20', '2025-06-18 02:02:03'),
(40, 'Jennifer', 'Hudson', 'customer', 'jlwest78@hotmail.com', '$2y$10$i1SKH2odxbwnsNj6mcfhOuGfKG0nJxic.U7Zwxp/1cYTC4SrYUGAO', '4985 Ellis Lane', 'Ellicott City', 'Maryland', '21043', 'Eastern Time', 'active', '4103367341', NULL, NULL, 'Subscribe', '0cSUnBBNpUwIlBCqwVRtA83SEIDBG9ollNx96F8J4SSaDvaAxJThTiNbR9pM', 'cus_LhFwXoTcg42C8I', 'Visa', '5615', 'tok_1KzrQnEjbxiB0vaPhOM4Hls1', '2020-11-11 19:23:52', '2022-05-16 00:05:06'),
(41, 'Bedri', 'Abubaker-Sharif', 'tutor', 'bedri.abubakersharif@gmail.com', '$2y$10$DzeLfHTNKJ.J.f6rPUgUQ.NAYIvXF7CI4XcHSDsn5Dl6d1di4H/zi', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Eastern Time', 'inactive', '443-279-8462', 'profile-1605485945-432613.jpg', 'I\'ve enjoyed teaching and tutoring math and science across all grade levels for many years. I joined the Smart Cookie Tutors team in 2019, and it\'s been incredibly rewarding. There is nothing quite like helping students grow in confidence and understanding. Outside of tutoring, I\'m an MD/PhD student, and enjoy playing soccer and reading books.', 'Subscribe', 'nn2rMxw0UIJO65n0GAMx7zv5z9Ui074s1JdqQvjRn2nrM1k3Sgpz287mZjDZ', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2020-11-12 22:00:17', '2025-02-04 01:29:04'),
(42, 'Rebecca', 'Etzine', 'tutor', 'rebecca.etzine@gmail.com', '$2y$10$zdVQPctFQdG7dZv5139AUOsEDDI2DSISTOvr3ybj.kxyNqtPyaP5i', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Eastern Time', 'inactive', '410-375-3655', 'profile-1605462632-74615.jpeg', 'Rebecca Etzine is a third-generation educator, following in the footsteps of her maternal grandparents, mother, and aunts. Growing up in Baltimore, Rebecca began assisting in classrooms at the age of 16 and has been teaching in some capacity ever since. Rebecca became the founding artistic director of The Cradle Theatre Company, a nonprofit, education-based theatre company at the age of 20. She led the company through six successful seasons while completing her dual degree in Performance and Directing at Fordham University and her post graduate teaching certificate at Trinity College, London. Rebecca holds a Master of Fine Arts degree in directing from The New School.  She worked with students in the South Bronx and Harlem for five years teaching film, playwriting, acting, improvisation, Shakespeare, and general academics.', 'Subscribe', 'ezK14AKe4N6yfvZLj6b2nfsS8PiLtu3XcBQY2ftsLsx9tCut1QVtxpZyA5gn', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2020-11-12 22:07:32', '2025-02-04 01:29:44'),
(43, 'Kelly', 'Housein', 'customer', 'kellyhousein@gmail.com', '$2y$10$YXHUchlkGIOMSUO74Q6Dq.1AbSsCUXgV4PY08euR5bRJRokkW2l6m', '10091 Hatbrim Ter', 'Columbia', 'Maryland', '21046', 'Eastern Time', 'active', '4435286429.', NULL, NULL, 'Subscribe', NULL, 'cus_K16YhcdyFIx7QK', 'Visa', '0211', 'tok_1JN4LoEjbxiB0vaPc1mFWA6v', '2020-11-16 20:03:59', '2021-08-10 23:27:20'),
(44, 'Sandra', 'Arias', 'tutor', 'sarias2015@gmail.com', '$2y$10$4aptTTYL1jS/7iucnY6yDeWiaSccMLX8NFetCjGO3BSFQGUHU8JfC', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Central Time', 'inactive', '872-600-0178', 'profile-1605902196-864670.jpeg', 'I enjoy teaching and tutoring children of all ages, and have lots of experience tutoring Spanish as well as elementary and middle school math and English.I had coached a local high school girls\' rugby team to victory in the state championships. When I\'m not working or coaching, I love to spend time with my children;often times spent in the library.', 'Subscribe', 'cyEmCp5zGDMWyrcFs7pNkQtWW0ycOpBNhYvpJ0jbv9a7If23xFDPERq6w7Yu', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2020-11-18 08:40:51', '2025-02-04 01:29:59'),
