(60, 'Kayla', 'Nemirovsky', 'tutor', 'knemir2@gmail.com', '$2y$10$H6slhWvEaG2ZTDMT1o7B1u8/4STHIcK/DXeEW/16KPpEVlNt.ohZG', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Eastern Time', 'active', '(410)419-3405', 'profile-1742232028-776555.jpg', 'Hi! My name is Kayla, I am a junior at UMBC and am majoring in math and financial economics. For as long as I can remember, math has been my favorite subject and I have wanted to be a teacher. When I was young, I used to lay out my stuffed animals and teach them- along with my unwilling little brother- how to add and subtract. To this day, I have a love for teaching and I am very excited to have the opportunity to share my love of math with others, who are human and willing this time! I have been working with students at Smart Cookie Tutors for 4 years and can\'t wait to work with you!', 'Subscribe', 'bpFoU0HMRZIaK5F4OpQKzkudJIZWdF4r5kuvY6CRZYUynpUthNl5S66vkCNq', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2021-01-08 07:28:43', '2025-03-17 22:20:42'),
